    <section id="postingbody">
        <div class="print-information print-qrcode-container">
            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="http://newyork.craigslist.org/mnh/fbh/6046987034.html"></div>
        </div>
After 14 successful years in South Florida we are bringing our expertise to New York. We have opened a steakhouse in the NoMad neighborhood and are looking for an experienced and passionate General Manager. This is an exciting opportunity for someone desiring a challenging, dynamic, yet stable work environment.<br>
<br>
Requirements for this position include:<br>
<br>
At least 3 years NYC fine dining experience as a General Manager (or at least 5 years in high­end hospitality management)<br>
<br>
A passion for customer satisfaction, hospitality, and food and drink<br>
<br>
Extensive wine knowledge<br>
<br>
Strong knowledge of state and federal employment, tax, safety, and health regulations (must have NYC DOH Food Handler's Certification)<br>
<br>
Exceptional leadership, managerial, and delegation skills<br>
<br>
Excellent verbal and written communication skills<br>
<br>
A verifiable track record of achievements with other restaurants<br>
<br>
Proficiency in Microsoft Word (Excel, Word, etc.)<br>
<br>
Knowledge of Aloha and OpenTable<br>
<br>
Outstanding organizational skills and instincts for superb food service<br>
<br>
All applicants must e­mail their resumes and cover letters attached. Compensation will be based on experience.<br>
<br>
Job Type: Full-time<br>
<br>
Required education:<br>
<br>
Bachelor's<br>
Required experience:<br>
<br>
GM: 3 years<br>
Required language:<br>
<br>
English    </section>

